OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,FKylie Minogue has told how her second
OL,8,Fcancer diagnosis in 2021 left her a
OL,9,F"shell of a person" and that she
OL,10,Fstruggled to find the "right time" to
OL,11,Ftell her fans.
OL,13,FThe Australian singer, known for Can't
OL,14,FGet You Out Of My Head and Spinning
OL,15,FAround, opened up about her second
OL,16,Fdiagnosis in her new three-part
OL,17,FNetflix series, titled Kylie.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
