OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,FMinogue, 57, was previously diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith early-stage breast cancer in May
OL,9,F2005, aged 36, and underwent a
OL,10,Flumpectomy and chemotherapy in Paris.
OL,12,FCoverage of her diagnosis led to an
OL,13,Funprecedented increase in bookings for
OL,14,Fmammograms, referred to as the "Kylie
OL,15,Feffect".
