OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779304271
OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,FNearly two decades after she received
OL,8,Fthe all-clear, the star opened up
OL,9,Fabout her second, more private, battle
OL,10,Fwith cancer, and reassured fans that
OL,11,Fshe had "got through it again, and all
OL,12,Fis well".
OL,14,F"My second cancer diagnosis was in
OL,15,Fearly 2021," the performer said. "I
OL,16,Fwas able to keep that to myself and go
OL,17,Fthrough that year not like the first
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,26,@sD@IOUtD@HO]vD@AOUwD@LO]wD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779304271
OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,F"(I've) been trying to find the right
OL,8,Ftime to say it. I don't feel obliged
OL,9,Fto tell the world, and actually, I
OL,10,Fjust couldn't at the time, because I
OL,11,Fwas just a shell of a person. I didn't
OL,12,Fwant to leave the house again at one
OL,13,Fpoint."
OL,15,FMinogue released her hit comeback
OL,16,Fsingle Padam Padam in 2023, which went
OL,17,Fon to win the Grammy Award for Best
OL,18,FPop Dance Recording.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
