OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779304271
OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,FShe added: "Padam Padam opened so many
OL,8,Fdoors for me, but on the inside I knew
OL,9,Fthat cancer wasn't just a blip in my
OL,10,Flife."
OL,12,FAppearing emotional, Minogue revealed
OL,13,Fthat her song Story, from her 2023
OL,14,Falbum, Tension, helped her mark that
OL,15,Ftime by writing "something that said
OL,16,Fwhat I wanted to say".
OL,18,FShe is later seen singing part of the
OL,19,Fsong: "I had a secret that I kept to
OL,20,Fmyself, yeah, I had a one-way ticket
OL,21,Fthat was goin' nowhere."
OL,26,@oD@LOUrD@FO]wD@QOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
