PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779304271
OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,FMinogue added: "I really just wanted
OL,8,Fto say what happened so I can let go
OL,9,Fof it. Thankfully, I got through it
OL,10,Fagain and all is well."
OL,12,FMinogue said the first time she was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with cancer, she postponed
OL,14,Fher chemotherapy in order to try to
OL,15,Ffall pregnant.
OL,17,FShe said: "There is so much more to
OL,18,Fcancer than just, 'you had it, you got
OL,19,Fthrough and you're fine ` you're fine
OL,20,Ffor now'.
OL,26,@oD@POUrD@WO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
