OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,F"I postponed my chemotherapy to try,
OL,8,Fwhich was quite scary at the time
OL,9,Fbecause you just want it out, gone. I
OL,10,Fdid try a few times with IVF. It was
OL,11,Fsuch a thread of hope. But I couldn't
OL,12,Fnot try.
OL,14,F"If it had happened, it would have
OL,15,Fbeen just shy of a miracle. but it
OL,16,Fdidn't work out that way. So this was
OL,17,Fa letter to what might've been."
