OL,3,CKylie Minogue says second cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis left her a 'shell of a
OL,5,Cperson'
OL,7,FHer sister, Dannii, added: "She's just
OL,8,Famazing with kids. She's always been
OL,9,Fgood with kids, just naturally
OL,10,Fincredible. I never saw myself as a
OL,11,Fparent and she always did, and that is
OL,12,Fheartbreaking."
OL,14,FThe docuseries follows Minogue's rise
OL,15,Fto fame from her early days starring
OL,16,Fin the Australian soap Neighbours
OL,17,Fthrough to her journey becoming one of
OL,18,Fpop's biggest stars.
